save_db_restr...der_batch_mode(25.10)    save_db_restr...der_batch_mode(25.10)

Name
       save_db_restrict_under_batch_mode

Syntax
        save_db_restrict_under_batch_mode {true | false}

       Type: integer

       Default: false

       Controls whether to save a database under the batch mode. By default, a
       new  database  is  saved  under the batch mode. However, if save_db_re-
       strict_under_batch_mode is set to true, the tool gives an error.

